org.cyclops.integratedcrafting.core.crafting.processoverride

Class CraftingProcessOverrideBrewingStand

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cyclops.integratedcrafting.core.crafting.processoverride.CraftingProcessOverrideBrewingStand
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICraftingProcessOverride

    public class CraftingProcessOverrideBrewingStand
extends java.lang.Object
implements ICraftingProcessOverride
    A crafting process override for brewing stands. This makes it so that items can be inserted from any slot, instead of the annoying side restrictions that vanilla adds.
